OL,3,CEyewitness describes frantic efforts
OL,4,Cto help knife attack victim
OL,6,FYou may find some of the details in
OL,7,Fthis report distressing.
OL,9,FA resident who witnessed a knife
OL,10,Fattack in Belfast has described what
OL,11,Fhe saw as like "something out of a
OL,12,Fmovie".
OL,14,FA man aged in his 40s has been left
OL,15,Fwith significant injuries to his face,
OL,16,Fneck and back according to the PSNI,
OL,17,Ffollowing the incident in the Kinnaird
OL,18,FAvenue area in the north of the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
