OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781394469
OL,3,CEyewitness describes frantic efforts
OL,4,Cto help knife attack victim
OL,6,FAnother man, aged in his 30s, has been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,8,Fmurder after the attack on Monday
OL,9,Fnight. Police said the arrested man is
OL,10,FSudanese.
OL,12,FAn eyewitness, who wanted to remain
OL,13,Fanonymous, told UTV he heard squealing
OL,14,Fand quickly realised "something wasn't
OL,15,Fright".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
