OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781394469
OL,3,CEyewitness describes frantic efforts
OL,4,Cto help knife attack victim
OL,6,FHe said his wife, who was obviously
OL,7,Fupset, told him about the attack,
OL,8,Fsaying "there's a guy on top of
OL,9,Fanother guy, and he's stabbing him....
OL,10,FI can hear the knife hitting the
OL,11,Fground".
OL,13,FThe witness described how he used his
OL,14,Fcar to try and stop the attacker by
OL,15,Frevving the engine in the hope to
OL,16,Fforce man to get off the victim.
OL,18,F"When I opened the door to get out, he
OL,19,Fpointed the knife at me while he was
OL,20,Fon top of the man."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
