PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781394469
OL,3,CEyewitness describes frantic efforts
OL,4,Cto help knife attack victim
OL,6,FHe said the attacker was treating the
OL,7,Fman "like a piece of meat" and he
OL,8,Frealised the urgency to try and help
OL,9,Fthe victim. As he looked for a weapon
OL,10,Fanother man had shown up to use a
OL,11,Fhurling stick to separate the pair.
OL,13,F"It was like something out of a movie.
OL,14,FIt was scary," he continued.
OL,16,FThe witness said there were words
OL,17,Fexchanged with the attacker but that
OL,18,Fhe couldn't understand what he was
OL,19,Fsaying.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
