PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781394469
OL,3,CEyewitness describes frantic efforts
OL,4,Cto help knife attack victim
OL,6,F"When I was there, he (the victim)
OL,7,Fwasn't responsive. He was lying face
OL,8,Fdown. It wasn't just an ordinary fight
OL,9,For incident."
OL,11,F"I'm looking in this guy's face, and
OL,12,Fall I could see was blood all round
OL,13,Fhis face.
OL,15,F"He just looked at me, and I just saw
OL,16,Fthe evilness in him.
OL,18,FHe described the hours since the
OL,19,Fattack as "absolute hell," adding "I
OL,20,Fwish I could have done more."
OL,26,@nD@WpmnD@bpn
